```

## Code-Konventionen

### Naming

| Typ | Pattern | Beispiel |
|-----|---------|----------|
| Komponenten | PascalCase + Suffix | `UserProfileCard.vue` |
| Composables | use + PascalCase | `useUserAuth.ts` |
| Stores | camelCase + Store | `userStore.ts` |
| Services | PascalCase + Service | `PaymentService.ts` |
| Types | PascalCase | `User.ts`, `ApiResponse.ts` |

### Komponenten-Template

```vue
